  "text": "Lower femoral BMD and whole body BMD have also been observed in patients with COPD, independent of treatment [CITATION_1] . The present investigation measured a lower femoral and middiaphyseal BMC in the Emp than in the Con group. The lower femoral BMC in the Emp group supports the hypothesis that the decreased BMD in COPD patients is due in part to the underlying disease and not the treatment regimen per se.",
